title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Someone might crash your party of one today. Otherwise, you are content to be on your own, whether you are chasing professional or personal interests. However, your party-crasher can add more to your process than you recognize at first. Relax and patiently take stock of exactly what you want to achieve now. You could discover youre lacking a skill or resource this other person is eager to provide. An unexpected collaboration may be the missing piece to your puzzle of the day. Novelist Ray Bradbury wrote, Creativity is a continual surprise. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
